<br>
This interface allows you to create and manage a message board between family members.<br>
<br>
Messages can be either sent to individuals or be left on a message board<br>
Create a new board by clicking on the "Add Message Board" link.<br>
Edit an existing board by clicking on its list on the left hand list.<br>
<br>
<u>Name</u>: Administrative short name to identify the board in the left hand list<br>
<u>Title</u>: Message Board title presented in the user interface<br>
<u>Sort</u>: Sort index to list the Boards<br>
<u>Is Online</u>: Tick off if the Message Board should not be displayed in the user interface<br>
<br>
<b>Messages</b> lists the messages currently posted on the Message Board.<br>
You may put them on or offline to relieve boards in the user interface.
